u <em>Touch !</em></h2>\n            <p class=\"mr-3 ml-3\">A <strong>Technology</strong> proposing an enterprise management by\n                by diving into the roots of your data to make it useful! And thus help\n                and decision-makers to integrate CSR, climate issues and their impacts into the heart of their\n                of their strategy.\n                <p>\n                With now 10 years of experience, we know how to go to the essence and target your needs to save you time and\n                save time and take concrete action on climate and CSR.\n                We have developed an approach that is both agile and respectful of the Bilan Carbone ® philosophy.\n                With Toovalu, climate and CSR become part of your strategy and become useful\n                and enlightening tools.\n\n            </p>\n            <p class=\"text-center pt-2 pb-2\"><a href=\"/a-propos-de-nous\" class=\"btn\">À propos de nous</a></p>\n            <div class=\"grid4 grid4-sm grid2-xs\">\n                <div class=\"text-center\">\n                    <p>Piloter</p><img src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/Groupe-79.png\" alt=\"toovalu-seminaire\" aria-label=\"toovalu-seminaire\">\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"text-center\">\n                    <p>Mettre en oeuvre</p><img src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/Groupe-89.png\" alt=\"toovalu-reportage-velo\" aria-label=\"toovalu-reportage-velo\">\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"text-center\">\n                    <p>Communiquer</p><img src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/Groupe-95.png\" alt=\"toovalu-marie-gaborit\" aria-label=\"toovalu-marie-gaborit\">\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"text-center\">\n                    <p>Engager</p><img src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/Groupe-98.png\" alt=\"toovalu-equipe-velo\" aria-label=\"toovalu-equipe-velo\">\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"grid4 grid2-sm\">\n        <div class=\"bg-blue\">\n            <h3 class=\"text-center\"><span class=\"text-center ff-light\">Un</span><span> BILAN CARBONE</span>\n            <p class=\"text-center ff-light\"> qui voit loin!</p>\n        </h3></div>\n        <div class=\"grid_fullcell\">\n            <img src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/HP_TT_BC-scaled.jpg\" alt=\"toovalu-seminaire\" aria-label=\"toovalu-seminaire\">\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"bg-pink\">\n            <h3 class=\"text-center\"><span class=\"text-center ff-light\">Construire votre</span><br>\n                <span>TRAJECTOIRE</span>\n                <br>BAS-CARBONE</h3>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"grid_fullcell\">\n            <img src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/HP_TT_Trajectoire.jpg\" alt=\"toovalu-reportage-velo\" aria-label=\"toovalu-reportage-velo\">\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"grid_fullcell\">\n            <img src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/HP_TT_Piloter-copie-retouch.jpg\" alt=\"toovalu-marie-gaborit\" aria-label=\"toovalu-marie-gaborit\">\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"bg-yellow\">\n            <h3 class=\"text-center\"><span>LEAD</span><br> <span> YOUR STRATEGIES</span><br>\n                <span class=\"text-center ff-light\">en toute sérénité!</span>\n            </h3><br>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"grid_fullcell\">\n            <img src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/HP_TT_Construction.jpg\" alt=\"toovalu-equipe-velo\" aria-label=\"toovalu-equipe-velo\">\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"bg-green\">\n            <h3 class=\"text-center\">\n                <span class=\"ff-light\">Un outil</span><br>\n                <span>COLLABORATIF <br>\n                            <span>&amp;</span>\n                            <br>\n                        <span>ENGAGÉ</span>\n                        </span>\n            </h3>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n    <hr>\n    <div class=\"content content\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <div class=\"wp-block-columns mb-0\">\n                <div class=\"wp-block-column flex-align-items\">\n                    <img src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/BCORP_logo.png\" alt=\"b-corp\" aria-label=\"b-corp-logo\">\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"wp-block-column\" style=\"flex-basis: 66%;\">\n                    <h3 class=\"mt-0\">Prenez part au mouvement des entreprises à impact positif !!\n                    </h3>\n                    <p class=\"text-center \">Toovalu est devenue BCorp en 2017, l\'une des premières à Nantes. Avec <a class=\"color-green pink-visited\" href=\"https://www.bcorporation.fr\">B-corp</a>\n                        , nous avons pour objectif de démontrer notre impact positif sur la société, et nous\n                        acceptons d’être évalués sur nos performances globales tous les deux ans</p>\n                    <p class=\"pt-2 bt-2\"><a href=\"/a-propos-de-nous\" class=\"btn\">En savoir +</a></p>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n    <hr>\n    <div class=\"testimonial\">\n        <h2 class=\"color-blue text-center\">\n            <em>Ils témoignent</em>\n        </h2>\n        <input type=\"radio\" name=\"slides\" id=\"radio-1\" checked=\"\">\n        <input type=\"radio\" name=\"slides\" id=\"radio-2\">\n        <input type=\"radio\" name=\"slides\" id=\"radio-3\">\n        <input type=\"radio\" name=\"slides\" id=\"radio-4\">\n        <ul class=\"slides\">\n            <li class=\"slide\">\n                <p><q>La rencontre entre l’expertise méthodologique et les fonctionnalités\n                        de l’outil TOOVALU crée la synergie\n                        nécessaire pour accompagner notre groupement dans la réduction de ses impacts.</q>\n                    <span class=\"author\">SYSTEME U<br>\n                                Jean-Michel GUILLOU responsable pôle QSSE Produits Fournisseurs\n                                </span>\n                </p>\n            </li>\n            <li class=\"slide\">\n                <p><q>Un outil fiable, traçable, simple, clair, efficace</q>\n                    <span class=\"author\">BNP PARIBAS REAL ESTATE </span>\n                </p>\n            </li>\n            <li class=\"slide\">\n                <p><q>Chez Toovalu, les formules proposées permettent\n                        à chaque entreprise de réussir\n                        sa DPEF quelque soit son degré de maturité. </q>\n                    <span class=\"author\">SFPI <br>\n                                Sophie Morel, Juriste et Administratrice Groupe</span>\n                </p>\n            </li>\n            <li class=\"slide\">\n                <p><q>L’outil TOOVALU transforme la contrainte DPEF en véritable opportunité de pilotage. Avec Toovalu,\n                        nous sommes passés d’une collecte d’indicateurs centralisée à un pilotage orienté métier.\n                        Chacun s’est approprié la plateforme et\n                        l’intègre pleinement dans son reporting</q>\n                    <span class=\"author\">HERIGE<br>\n                                Caroline Lutinier Responsable RSE</span>\n                </p>\n            </li>\n        </ul>\n        <div class=\"slidesNavigation\">\n            <label for=\"radio-1\" id=\"dotForRadio-1\"></label>\n            <label for=\"radio-2\" id=\"dotForRadio-2\"></label>\n            <label for=\"radio-3\" id=\"dotForRadio-3\"></label>\n            <label for=\"radio-4\" id=\"dotForRadio-4\"></label>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n    <!-- #main -->\n    <!-- #primary -->\n<!-- /wp:html -->','home en','','inherit','closed','closed','','1851-revision-v1','','','2021-10-27 14:50:35','2021-10-27 14:50:35','',1851,'http://testsite2.local/?p=1870',0,'revision','',0);
INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES (1872,1,'2021-10-28 08:46:42','2021-10-28 08:46:42','<!-- wp:html -->\n<div id=\"primary\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/html\">\n        <main id=\"main\">\n            <div class=\"content banniere\">\n                <img class=\"wdt-100\" src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/1024x450px_Concentre_de_technologie_pour_entreprises_conscientes.png\" alt=\"claim-entreprise-consciente\" aria-label=\"claim-entreprise-consciente\">\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"container\">\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"pb-4\">\n                <h2 class=\"text-center\"><em>Toovalu</em> propose</h2>\n                <p class=\"text-center ml-15 mr-15\">Une gamme de solution logicielle<br>\n                    au service de l\'engagement des entreprises. L\'outil qui vous emmène au-delà du reporting !\n                </p>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"grid2 pb-4\">\n                    <div>\n                        <h2 class=\"text-center pb-1\"><em>Climat</em></h2>\n                        <p class=\"text-center\"><strong>Toovalu rend l\'engagement climat accessible à tous !</strong>\n                        </p>\n                        <div class=\"flex align-items-start pb-2\">\n                            <img class=\"mt-05 ml-5 mr-3\" src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/right-arrow.png\" alt=\"\">\n                            <p class=\"mb-0 mr-3\">Module Bilan Carbone - collaboratif, multi-site, simplifié et ergonomique, une analyse détaillée de vos données</p>\n                        </div>\n                        <div class=\"flex align-items-start pb-2\">\n                            <img class=\"mt-05 ml-5 mr-3\" src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/right-arrow.png\" alt=\"\">\n                            <p class=\"mb-0 mr-3\">Module stratégie climat - Définir vos objectifs, votre plan d\'action, votre trajectoire Bas-carbone !</p>\n                        </div>\n\n                    </div>\n                    <div>\n                        <h2 class=\"text-center pb-1\"><em>RSE</em></h2>\n                        <p class=\"text-center\"><strong>Faire de votre DPEF, un outil de pilotage.</strong></p>\n                        <div class=\"flex align-items-start pb-2\">\n                            <img class=\"mt-05 ml-5 mr-3\" src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/right-arrow.png\" alt=\"\">\n                            <p class=\"mb-0 mr-3\">Module RSE - collecter vos données extra-financières de façon collaborative et intuitive, pilotez vos objectifs et votre plan d\'action.</p>\n                        </div>\n                        <div class=\"flex align-items-start pb-2\">\n                            <img class=\"mt-05 ml-5 mr-3\" src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/right-arrow.png\" alt=\"\">\n                            <p class=\"mb-0 mr-3\">Stratégie de performance globale - nous vous apportons les solutions pour aller plus loin, vers une entreprise à impact positif !\n                            </p>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n            </div>\n            <h2 class=\"text-center\">Vos <em>bénéfices</em> avec Toovalu</h2>\n            <div class=\"text-center img-hover-zoom\">\n                <img class=\"zoom-img\" src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/Trace-140.png\" alt=\"\">\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"grid2 mt-7\">\n                <div class=\"grid_fullcell\">\n                    <div class=\"\">\n                        <img src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/SOL_-scaled.jpeg\" alt=\"toovalu-reportage-impact\" aria-label=\"toovalu-reportage-impact\">\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                <div>\n                    <h2 class=\"text-center pb-2\"><em>Vous êtes . . . </em></h2>\n                    <div class=\"flex align-items-start pb-2\">\n                        <img class=\"mt-05 ml-5 mr-3\" src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/right-arrow.png\" alt=\"\">\n                        <p class=\"mb-0 mr-3\">Dirigeant engagé, Responsable RSE motivé,  référent climat-environnement,\n                            acteur volontaire pour contribuer à la transformation de votre entreprise...</p>\n                    </div>\n                    <div class=\"flex align-items-start pb-2\">\n                        <img class=\"mt-05 ml-5 mr-3\" src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/right-arrow.png\" alt=\"\">\n                        <p class=\"mb-0 mr-3\">Concerné par l’empreinte carbone de votre entreprise ou par la DPEF.<br>\n                            Peut-être, avez-vous déjà̀ structuré votre stratégie RSE/Climat\n                            en identifiant vos axes d’engagement, vos risques et vos enjeux prioritaires ? </p>\n                    </div>\n                    <div class=\"flex align-items-start pb-2\">\n                        <img class=\"mt-05 ml-5 mr-3\" src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/right-arrow.png\" alt=\"\">\n                        <p class=\"mb-0 mr-3\">Bravo, Vous avez déjà lancé un premier Bilan carbone, une démarche RSE, des actions RSE dans votre entreprise et vous souhaitez aller plus loin !</p>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"text-center img-hover-zoom\">\n                <img class=\"zoom-img\" src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/Trace-139.png\" alt=\"toovalu-impact-reportage\" aria-label=\"toovalu-impact-reportage\">\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"grid2 mt-5\">\n                <div>\n                    <h2 class=\"text-center pb-2\"><em>Vous souhaitez</em></h2>\n                    <div class=\"flex align-items-start pb-2\">\n                        <img class=\"mt-05 ml-5 mr-3\" src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/right-arrow.png\" alt=\"\">\n                        <p class=\"mb-0\"><strong>Structurer </strong>votre démarche d\'engagement pour en faire un axe stratégique de votre entreprise\n                            </p>\n                    </div>\n                    <div class=\"flex align-items-start pb-2\">\n                        <img class=\"mt-05 ml-5 mr-3\" src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/right-arrow.png\" alt=\"\">\n                        <p class=\"mb-0\"><strong>Gagner</strong> du temps à la collecte, l’audit et l’exploitation des données.\n                        </p>\n                    </div>\n                    <div class=\"flex align-items-start pb-2\">\n                        <img class=\"mt-05 ml-5 mr-3\" src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/right-arrow.png\" alt=\"\">\n                        <p class=\"mb-0\">Avoir une démarche climat robuste, crédible et inscrite dans la durée en cohérence avec les trajectoires 1,5°C du GIEC</p>\n                    </div>\n                    <div class=\"flex align-items-start pb-2\">\n                        <img class=\"mt-05 ml-5 mr-3\" src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/right-arrow.png\" alt=\"\">\n                        <p class=\"mb-0\"><strong>Convaincre, impliquer</strong> toutes vos parties prenantes.\n                            <strong>Passer à l’action</strong> et <strong>s’engager</strong> sur la durée</p>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"grid_fullcell\">\n                    <div class=\"\">\n                        <img src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/Toovalu_Reportage_6-scaled.jpeg\" alt=\"toovalu-impact-reportage\" aria-label=\"toovalu-impact-reportage\">\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"text-center img-hover-zoom\">\n                <img class=\"zoom-img\" src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/Trace-140.png\" alt=\"\">\n            </div>\n            <h2 class=\"text-center pb-2\">Toovalu est fait <br><em>pour vous !</em></h2>\n            <div class=\"content\">\n                <div class=\"container pt-2 pb-2\">\n                    <h3 class=\"text-center\">L\'outil qui va mettre un coup de froid sur le réchauffement climatique !</h3>\n                    <div>\n                        <div class=\"flex-space-around pb-2\">\n                            <a href=\"#dynamique\">Tableau de bord dynamique</a>\n                            <a href=\"#collecte\">Vos axes stratégiques</a>\n                            <a href=\"#analyse\">Vos indicateurs de pilotage</a>\n                        </div>\n                        <div class=\"carousel\">\n                            <ul class=\"slides\">\n                                <input type=\"radio\" name=\"radio-buttons\" id=\"img-1\" checked=\"\">\n                                <li class=\"slide-container\" id=\"dynamique\">\n                                    <div class=\"slide-image\">\n                                        <img src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/image-5-1.png\">\n                                    </div>\n                                    <div class=\"carousel-controls\">\n                                        <label for=\"img-3\" class=\"prev-slide\">\n                                            <span><img class=\"wt-2\" src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/right-arrow-1.png\" <=\"\" span=\"\">\n                                        </span></label>\n                                        <label for=\"img-2\" class=\"next-slide\">\n                                            <span><img class=\"wt-2\" src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/right-arrow.png\"></span>\n                                        </label>\n                                    </div>\n                                </li>\n                                <input type=\"radio\" name=\"radio-buttons\" id=\"img-2\">\n                                <li class=\"slide-container\" id=\"collecte\">\n                                    <div class=\"slide-image\">\n                                        <img src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/image-6-1.png\">\n                                    </div>\n                                    <div class=\"carousel-controls\">\n                                        <label for=\"img-1\" class=\"prev-slide\">\n                                            <span><img class=\"wt-2\" src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/right-arrow-1.png\" <=\"\" span=\"\">\n                                        </span></label>\n                                        <label for=\"img-3\" class=\"next-slide\">\n                                            <span><img class=\"wt-2\" src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/right-arrow.png\"></span>\n                                        </label>\n                                    </div>\n                                </li>\n                                <input type=\"radio\" name=\"radio-buttons\" id=\"img-3\">\n                                <li class=\"slide-container\" id=\"analyse\">\n                                    <div class=\"slide-image\">\n                                        <img src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/image-4.png\">\n                                    </div>\n                                    <div class=\"carousel-controls\">\n                                        <label for=\"img-2\" class=\"prev-slide\">\n                                            <span><img class=\"wt-2\" src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/right-arrow-1.png\" <=\"\" span=\"\">\n                                        </span></label>\n                                        <label for=\"img-1\" class=\"next-slide\">\n                                            <span><img class=\"wt-2\" src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/right-arrow.png\"></span>\n                                        </label>\n                                    </div>\n                                </li>\n                                <div class=\"carousel-dots\">\n                                    <label for=\"img-1\" class=\"carousel-dot\" id=\"img-dot-1\"></label>\n                                    <label for=\"img-2\" class=\"carousel-dot\" id=\"img-dot-2\"></label>\n                                    <label for=\"img-3\" class=\"carousel-dot\" id=\"img-dot-3\"></label>\n                                </div>\n                            </ul>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"flex-space-around pt-2 pb-4\">\n                <a href=\"/contact/\" class=\"btn btn-appel-action a\">Demandez une démo</a>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"grid2 height-solutions pb-4\">\n                <div class=\"bg-green\">\n                    <div class=\"flex-center flex-align-items pt-4\">\n                        <img class=\"mt-05 ml-5 mr-3\" src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/Groupe-105.png\" alt=\"\">\n                        <p class=\"mb-0\"><strong>MOINS</strong> de temps<br> passé à collecter<br> et analyser\n                            vos\n                            données,</p>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"bg-pink\">\n                    <div class=\"flex-center flex-align-items pt-4\">\n                        <img class=\"mt-05 ml-5 mr-3\" src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/Groupe-110.png\" alt=\"\">\n                        <p class=\"mb-0\">c’est <strong>PLUS</strong> de temps<br> pour mettre en œuvre votre<br>\n                            stratégie.<strong></strong></p>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"testimonial block-solutions\">\n                <h2 class=\"color-blue text-center\">\n                    <em>Ils témoignent</em>\n                </h2>\n                <input type=\"radio\" name=\"slides\" id=\"radio-1\" checked=\"\">\n                <input type=\"radio\" name=\"slides\" id=\"radio-2\">\n                <input type=\"radio\" name=\"slides\" id=\"radio-3\">\n                <input type=\"radio\" name=\"slides\" id=\"radio-4\">\n                <ul class=\"slides\">\n                    <li class=\"slide\">\n                        <p><q>Pour nous faciliter la collecte et la consolidation de nos données extra-financières dans le Groupe, nous utilisons l’outil TOOVALU depuis fin 2017.Cet outil a été adapté en co-construction pour coller au mieux à nos spécificités. Perçu comme simple d’utilisation,\n                                ergonomique et souple par tous les utilisateurs.\n                                Dont l’auditeur extra-financier!</q>\n                            <span class=\"author\">GROUPE SOPREMA<br>\n                                Olivier Weymann Directeur Stratégie et Performance Environnementale                                </span>\n                        </p>\n                    </li>\n                    <li class=\"slide\">\n                        <p><q>Un outil fiable, traçable, simple, clair, efficace</q>\n                            <span class=\"author\">BNP PARIBAS REAL ESTATE </span>\n                        </p>\n                    </li>\n                    <li class=\"slide\">\n                        <p><q>Chez Toovalu, les formules proposées permettent\n                                à chaque entreprise de réussir\n                                sa DPEF quelque soit son degré de maturité. </q>\n                            <span class=\"author\">SFPI <br>\n                                Sophie Morel, Juriste et Administratrice Groupe</span>\n                        </p>\n                    </li>\n                    <li class=\"slide\">\n                        <p><q>L’outil TOOVALU transforme la contrainte DPEF en véritable opportunité de pilotage. Avec Toovalu, nous sommes passés d’une collecte d’indicateurs centralisée à un pilotage orienté métier.\n                                Chacun s’est approprié la plateforme et\n                                l’intègre pleinement dans son reporting</q>\n                            <span class=\"author\">HERIGE<br>\n                                Caroline Lutinier Responsable RSE</span>\n                        </p>\n                    </li>\n                </ul>\n                <div class=\"slidesNavigation\">\n                    <label for=\"radio-1\" id=\"dotForRadio-1\"></label>\n                    <label for=\"radio-2\" id=\"dotForRadio-2\"></label>\n                    <label for=\"radio-3\" id=\"dotForRadio-3\"></label>\n                    <label for=\"radio-4\" id=\"dotForRadio-4\"></label>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </main><!-- #main -->\n    </div><!-- #primary -->\n<!-- /wp:html -->','Nos Solutions','','inherit','closed','closed','','62-revision-v1','','','2021-10-28 08:46:42','2021-10-28 08:46:42','',62,'http://testsite2.local/?p=1872',0,'revision','',0);
