>Touch !</em></h2>\n            <p class=\"mr-3 ml-3\"><strong>Technology</strong> proposing a management of the company by the impact by plunging to the roots of your data to make them useful! And thus helping the leaders and decision-markers to integrate CSR, climate issues and their impacts at the heart of their strategy.\n                </p><p>\n                With now 10 years of experience, we know how to go to the point and target your needs to save you time and act concretely on the climate and CSR.\n                We have developed an approach both agile and respecting the philosophy of th Carbon® balance.\n                With TOOVALU, climate & CSR integrate your strategy and become useful\n                and illuminating steering tools.\n\n            </p>\n            <p class=\"text-center pt-2 pb-2\"><a href=\"/a-propos-de-nous\" class=\"btn\">À propos de nous</a></p>\n            <div class=\"grid4 grid4-sm grid2-xs\">\n                <div class=\"text-center\">\n                    <p>Pilot</p><img src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/Groupe-79.png\" alt=\"toovalu-seminar\" aria-label=\"toovalu-seminaire\">\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"text-center\">\n                    <p>Enforce</p><img src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/Groupe-89.png\" alt=\"toovalu-report-bicycle\" aria-label=\"toovalu-reportage-velo\">\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"text-center\">\n                    <p>Communicate</p><img src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/Groupe-95.png\" alt=\"toovalu-marie-gaborit\" aria-label=\"toovalu-marie-gaborit\">\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"text-center\">\n                    <p>To hire</p><img src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/Groupe-98.png\" alt=\"toovalu-equipe-velo\" aria-label=\"toovalu-equipe-velo\">\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"grid4 grid2-sm\">\n        <div class=\"bg-blue\">\n            <h3 class=\"text-ce